---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Peptide News - What's Happening in the Research Peptide World"
description: "News and analysis on research peptides, FDA approvals, clinical developments, regulatory changes, and what it all means for the research community."
ogTitle: "Peptide News | Peptide Price Lab"
ogDescription: "News and analysis on research peptides, FDA approvals, clinical developments, and what's changing in the peptide world."
schema:
  "@context": "https://schema.org"
  "@type": "CollectionPage"
  name: "Peptide News"
  description: "News and analysis on research peptides from Peptide Price Lab."
  url: "https://peptidepricelab.com/news/"
  publisher:
    "@type": "Organization"
    name: "Peptide Price Lab"
    url: "https://peptidepricelab.com"
---

<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
  <a href="/">Home</a>
  <span>&rsaquo;</span>
  News
</nav>

<div class="news-page">
  <header class="article-header">
    <div class="eyebrow">Peptide News</div>
    <h1>What's happening in the <em>peptide world</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">
      FDA actions, clinical updates, regulatory changes, and what they actually mean for researchers and the broader peptide community. Our own weekly take lives in <a href="/dispatch/">the Dispatch</a>; this is everyone else's headlines, annotated.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="article-list">
    {% for article in collections.news %}
      {% set dek = article.data.cardDek or article.data.description %}
      {% set when = article.data.date or article.data.schema.datePublished %}
      {% set cat = article.data.category or "News" %}
      <a href="{{ article.url }}" class="article-card{% if article.data.image %} article-card-with-image{% endif %}">
        {% if article.data.image %}
          <div class="article-card-image">
            <img src="{{ article.data.image }}" alt="{{ article.data.imageAlt or article.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="article-card-content">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="card-tag">{{ cat }}</span>
            {% if when %}<span>{{ when | readableDate }}{% if article.data.readingTime %} &middot; {{ article.data.readingTime }}{% endif %}</span>{% endif %}
          </div>
          <h2>{{ article.data.h1 or article.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if dek %}<p>{{ dek }}</p>{% endif %}
          <span class="read-more">Read more &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% else %}
      <p class="microcopy">No news posts yet. Check back soon.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {% set pledgeVariant = "wide" %}
  {% include "partials/pledge.njk" %}
</div>
